 Participants beat drums during the Hit the Beat event at Wolwedans Village, located in the desert plains of the NamibRand Nature Reserve in Namibia on March 12, 2022. Young talented individuals from diverse cultures of the world engaged in artistic creativity during the annual Hit the Beat event at Wolwedans Village. (Photo by Musa Zimunya/Xinhua)  Participants sing during the Hit the Beat event at Wolwedans Village, located in the desert plains of the NamibRand Nature Reserve in Namibia on March 12, 2022. Young talented individuals from diverse cultures of the world engaged in artistic creativity during the annual Hit the Beat event at Wolwedans Village. (Photo by Musa Zimunya/Xinhua)